# Ownership map. GitHub requests reviews from the owning party when matching
# files change. Tighten as the team grows; today the maintainer owns everything.

# Default owner for anything not matched below.
*                       @your-org/maintainers

# The source of truth and architecture docs get extra scrutiny.
/.claude/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md   @your-org/maintainers
/docs/architecture/          @your-org/maintainers

# Build system and CI.
/CMakeLists.txt         @your-org/maintainers
/cmake/                 @your-org/maintainers
/.github/               @your-org/maintainers

# The public ABI — never changes without a maintainer + an ADR.
/include/               @your-org/maintainers
